## Steps to reproduce the issue

`./yosys -p 'prep; opt -full -fine; stat` 

```
module top(input [1:0] i, output [1:0] o);
wire [3:0] t;
assign t = i * 3;
assign o = t / 3;
endmodule
```

## Expected behavior

Should boil down to `assign o = i;`

## Actual behavior

`$mul` cell followed by `$div` cell: [show.pdf](https://github.com/YosysHQ/yosys/files/3069715/show.pdf)

